 some notes is recommended, but not required for participation.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>More information on assigned content for this session to be announced.</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>Accessibility</strong></h3>\n\n<p>UCSF welcomes all participants to our events. If you need a reasonable accommodation to participate in this event because of a disability, please contact Eileen Chen at eileen.chen@ucsf.edu as soon as possible.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><strong>People</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li><strong>Eileen Chen</strong> is an Education and Research Librarian. She supports literature searching, AI, and open access publishing.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Geoff Boushey </strong>is a Data Science Specialist. He teaches with Python, SQL, machine learning, and AI, with an emphasis on document, text, and media analysis.</li>\n\t<li><strong>Yea-Hung Chen</strong> is a Data Science Specialist. He provides support on R, data science, and AI to the UCSF community.</li>\n</ul>","url":{"public":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/event/16753085","admin":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/aevent.php?c=928&m=edit&event_id=16753085"},"location":"FAMRI Library","category":[{"id":86724,"name":"AI"},{"id":27094,"name":"Data Science"}],"owner":{"id":133839,"name":"Eileen Chen"},"presenter":"","calendar":{"id":928,"name":"Library Events and Classes","public":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/calendar/events","admin":"https://calendars.library.ucsf.edu/admin/calendar/928"},"seats":50,"registration":true,"registration_form_id":0,"registration_series_linked":false,"has_registration_opened":true,"registration_open_at":"2026-04-17T15:24:58-07:00","has_registration_closed":false,"registration_close_at":"2026-08-12T15:00:00-07:00","physical_seats":50,"physical_seats_taken":15,"online_seats":0,"online_seats_taken":0,"seats_taken":15,"wait_list":false,"color":"#058488","featured_image":"","featured_image_alt_text":"","geolocation":null,"future_dat